    <j.2:build_info>reception-ID: PO-20190313-2397; environment: PROD; newCERES: 3.23.2; IMMC2CDM: 2.8.0; rules: preleg/rules-consil.xml#39852#2018-05-06; builddate: 2019-03-13T17:19:18.032;</j.2:build_info>
